Description:
We are visionary urban developers dedicated to creating vibrant, thoughtfully designed communities that harmonize modern innovation with timeless values. Our projects seamlessly blend work, life, and play, fostering lasting connections and enhancing San Diego's vitality.
Key Focus Areas:

// Future-built, profit-focused development
// Creation of inclusive, thriving urban spaces
// Innovative design blending modern elegance with urban vitality
// Strong returns for investors
// Sustainable and community-oriented projects

At ELDA, we're not just constructing buildings; we're crafting stories and reimagining urban living. Our passion lies in developing spaces that drive equity, foster community connections, and secure long-term growth.

Community Energy Wales is a not for profit membership organisation that has been set up to provide assistance and a voice to community groups working on energy projects in Wales. We want to help create the conditions in Wales that allow community energy projects to flourish, and communities to prosper.

